							With a built-in wysiwyg editor, you can write and
							format your content without <a class="underline"
								>leaving</a
							> the platform. Focus on your words, not on markdown syntax
							or external tools.
						</p>
						<a class="flex items-center gap-2"
							>link stuff <ArrowRight className="size-4" />
						</a>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div
					class="heroText mt-8 md:mt-15 relative p-4 md:p-14 overflow-hidden md:rounded-[30px] rounded-[20px] h-full"
