						<p class="text-muted-foreground">
							With a built-in wysiwyg editor, you can write and
							format your content without <a class="underline"
								>leaving</a
							> the platform. Focus on your words, not on markdown syntax
							or external tools.
						</p>
					</div>
				</div>

				<Integrations4 hideText />

				<div class="flex flex-col gap-5">
